node.text:
The Salt Cave at @islandwellnesscenter is my favorite spot to chill in Rhode Island! 

It’s so magical! 🥰

You can reserve your own private time at the Island Wellness Center:

 420 friendly for after hours! ✨

Weeknights 6-8pm and weekends 4-6pm. 

📸: @caseysanginario 

#weedqueen_official #rhodeisland #islandwellnesscenter #braziliangirl #chill
